Board description
-----------------
Clock rate:	40 - 66 MHz, depending on CPU
Bus width:	16 bit Flash, 32 bit DRAM
FLASH:		128K - 1024K, 120ns
RAM:		2 - 32M DRAM SIMM, autodetects size and speed

